description: Yesterday I visited again the suburbs of Prague. A young client with a migrational background called me that he had serious financial issues. As his voice sounded very young and cute I was ready to help him even with a higher amount. When I arrived my mood changed as he was living in the top-floor and the elevator didn´t work. But his flat looked surprisingly clean and tidy. And when he told me about the amount he needed I was surprised that it wasn´t so high either. But he needed it urgently. his debts were not about a loan from a bank but from a private "company". And these guys know how to get back their money. And when I told him about my little money-for-sex offer he didn´t hesitate too much. Actually he almost didn´t hesitate at all...
title: Debt Dandy 89
